Sorry, I don't have a good answer for your question, but I do have a question for you.  You mention you have 14 mind at lvl 26, that gives you the spell:<P>Blanket of Senility (Domination)<BR>Gained at level 14<BR>33 sec. Mesmerize, 4 ft. radius <P>You mention rooting, and that your root durations halve with each cast, and that that's a problem for your soloing.  You don't mention mezzing, which is separate from rooting - you can root for full duration, then mez for full duration, etc.  Are you doing that and you just didn't mention it?  If so, never mind.  If not, that will help your soloing.<P>Nicke Danger 20 Sorc
